'From Squeak3.2alpha of 2 October 2001 [latest update: #4435] on 16 October 2001 at 8:26:41 pm'!"Change Set:		RunArrayFix-arDate:			16 October 2001Author:			Andreas RaabFixes a typo from the last CS."!!RunArray methodsFor: 'adding' stamp: 'ar 10/16/2001 20:25'!addLast: value	"Add value as the last element of the receiver."	lastIndex _ nil.  "flush access cache"	(runs size=0 or: [values last ~= value])	  ifTrue:		[runs _ runs copyWith: 1.		values _ values copyWith: value]	  ifFalse:		[runs at: runs size put: runs last+1]! !